items.description: 基于Transformer和torch等框架，参考TrOCR论文和官方开源代码，自己复现出的TrOCR项目，可load官方预训练权重。  Based on frameworks such as Transformer and torch, and referring to the TrOCR paper and the official open-source code, I have independently reproduced the TrOCR project, which can load the official pre-trained weights.

items.name: EFF-Monitoring
items.description: EFF-Monitoring（Efficient Monitoring，高效监控），是一款面向安全运营 / 蓝队的本地告警处理工具，聚焦“高效日志处理 + 自动化情报补全 + AI 研判”，帮助安全监测人员在攻防演练和日常值班中快速看懂告警、打通上下游。
